{"tid":2512293,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[7-11自拍賓周] 男店員疑當值期間露體拍不雅照上網 警方接獲便利店報案","createTime":"2021-05-01T14:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T05:46:39.000Z","uid":3189,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ab71aedd417efdfc622a64b51734e108630012b7","tid":2512293,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/none/c30bef53225382ab06f66b8f6cbf6d5a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210501/_2021050122190813459.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2Fc30bef53225382ab06f66b8f6cbf6d5a%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210501%2F_2021050122190813459.jpg&h=4df1d16e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n便利店男店員疑當值期間露體拍不雅照並上載。網上截圖<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳近日一批照片，懷疑是連鎖便利店男員工於店內身穿制服露體。<br />\n<br />\n社交網站Twitter上一名網民，疑在工作期間於7-Eleven便利店內拍下多張不雅照片，包括在擺放冷藏貨物的冷凍房脫下褲子露出內褲，又於員工休息室拍下不雅照片。<br />\n<br />\n涉事男子已經關閉有關社交賬號，翻查記錄，男子至少在今年1月3日、2月2日、3月20日，於Twitter發布貼文及照片。<br />\n<br />\n帖文帶有性挑逗含義，指「做做下嘢大膽影返幾張先，唔知有無CCTV影到呢」、「今晚試下入雪房露X，睇下X唔X到先」、「雪房真係好凍，差啲X唔起」、「雪房真係好凍，X小小算係交到功課喇，你哋收唔收貨先」、「今晚返工，響倉影咩嘢相好呢，你地有冇好提議」、「今晚試吓起倉露下先，有咩建議」、「暫時放到咁大尺度喇」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/none/277e6d6fd2a60262b42aba5bb2a8483d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210501/_2021050122190914503.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F277e6d6fd2a60262b42aba5bb2a8483d%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210501%2F_2021050122190914503.jpg&h=03ccf1fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n便利店男店員疑當值期間露體拍不雅照並上載。網上截圖<br />\n<br />\n連鎖便利店今日回應傳媒稱，已將個別事件報警處理，公司將嚴肅跟進事件，並會一如以往確保員工和顧客安全。<br />\n<br />\n警方今日接獲報案指發現網上流傳照片，有一名男子懷疑在店鋪內作出不雅行為。經初步調查，案件列作求警調查，交由大埔警區人員跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/none/3e977d21c23b2099b445753da44cb621/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210501/_2021050122190927521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F3e977d21c23b2099b445753da44cb621%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210501%2F_2021050122190927521.jpg&h=b2c74875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/none/5b2f3618e848fd5a25d5cede3816fe9d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210501/_2021050121420942189.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F5b2f3618e848fd5a25d5cede3816fe9d%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210501%2F_2021050121420942189.jpg&h=cf029ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/none/7fd5d3ac1d58ae4909f32f7a9e0d33b1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210501/_2021050121421172229.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F7fd5d3ac1d58ae4909f32f7a9e0d33b1%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210501%2F_2021050121421172229.jpg&h=968dcf88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/none/e4b5fe4cdcea3aa4f6e98b2d37be3b1a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210501/_2021050121421087677.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2Fe4b5fe4cdcea3aa4f6e98b2d37be3b1a%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210501%2F_2021050121421087677.jpg&h=79f045f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/none/61b80ab65e143305d19673c18178e816/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210501/_2021050121420917906.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F61b80ab65e143305d19673c18178e816%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210501%2F_2021050121420917906.jpg&h=ea01bee6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41621a4ff0a5a94c6676a10b7ff43b3a15645825","tid":2512293,"uid":54681,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:39:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-larg